ABOUT
contact
SERVICE
Hi there, I am Gulsah!
I am a web developer producing
creative and professional solutions for your online presence.
MacBook Air

WHAT I DO

As a freelance web developer, I create expressive and functional websites. My clients range from agencies and companies to individuals from all over the world. I am flexible and capable of working on projects of all sizes.

Scroll and click through the following options to learn more about each service.

01
Website Design and Development
what's ıncluded → HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Next.js, Figma, Adobe XD
—
Wireframing, prototyping, and iterative design processes are integral parts of this service, resulting in web experiences that stand out and resonate with users. The use of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, and Next.js guarantees a smooth user journey across devices and browsers.
—
Moreover, I provide a diverse spectrum of web solutions. Clients seeking expedited and streamlined web development can benefit from my utilization of platforms such as Webflow. Webflow stands out as an exceptional option for the creation of straightforward, user-friendly websites that consistently uphold a refined and professional aesthetic.
—
Craft visually appealing and user-friendly websites that seamlessly blend innovative design with modern web development technologies. From concept to creation, I create custom, responsive, and interactive websites that cater to your unique requirements. By utilizing a human-centered design approach, I ensure that the interfaces are intuitive and engaging for your target audience.
02
Database Management and Integration
what's ıncluded → MongoDB, SQL
—
Leverage the power of MongoDB and SQL to seamlessly manage and integrate databases into your web applications. From data collection and storage to retrieval, I ensure efficient data management that supports your business processes. I design robust database architectures and implement optimized querying strategies for superior performance.
—
Continuous maintenance and updates guarantee smooth operations.
03
User-Centered Design
what's ıncluded → Integration of Human-Centered Web Experiences
—
Craft user experiences that prioritize your audience's needs through Human-Centered Design principles. In-depth Design Research and Usability Testing lead to interfaces that resonate with users, enhancing their interactions. Every design decision is informed by user insights and feedback.
—
Additionally, I offer regular website revisions and updates based on user feedback and evolving trends.
04
SEO (Search Engine Optimization)
what's ıncluded → Strategic Web Usability SEO
—
Elevate your online presence with strategic Web Usability SEO. Combining coding proficiency with SEO best practices, I enhance your website's visibility on search engines. From keyword optimization to on-page SEO elements, I ensure improved rankings and organic traffic.
—
Ongoing SEO adjustments adapt to evolving search engine algorithms.
05
Website Revisions and Updates
what's ıncluded → Skillful HTML, CSS, JavaScript Refinements
—
Your website's journey doesn't end after launch; it's an ongoing evolution. I facilitate seamless updates and revisions to accommodate your evolving needs.
—
This service encompasses adding new pages, integrating novel features, design improvements, boosting performance, and refining user interactions.
—
Through HTML, CSS, and JavaScript refinements, I ensure your website consistently adapts, ensuring its relevance and engagement in line with the dynamic requirements of your users. Your site will always be at the forefront of delivering an exceptional online experience.
let's work together
I collaborate with agencies, companies, and individuals from around the globe. No project is too big or small for me—I'm ready to work on all of them.

get in touch




I am Gulsah Deger,

a passionate web developer based in Turkey. I have a Bachelor's degree in Computer Engineering, and I have transitioned from coding processes in Business Intelligence for a global construction company to pursuing my love for web development as a freelancer.

MY APPROACH
With a deep appreciation for art, technology, and culture, I approach every project with curiosity and a commitment to user-friendly design. Drawing inspiration from diverse sources, I strive to provide unique and discerning solutions. I am always eager to collaborate and exchange ideas, so feel free to reach out if you would like to work together.
